年 5 月起担任格力电器的董事长兼总裁，这位商界「铁娘子」带领格力电器跨越了 2000 亿元的门槛，从空调业扩张到精密机床、工业机器人、新能源等领域，以及冰箱、洗衣机等白电业务，变为多元化的工业集团。 格力电器如何推进管理层的年轻化，成为投资者关心的热点之一。董明珠回应称，格力重视人才培养，不是以年龄、资历来衡量，关键在于人才的思想要保持年轻化，有创新能力、责任心及敢于拼搏。 「绝不用海归派，只在国内高校里培养自己的人才。」董明珠连任董事长称「绝不用海归」，张伟升任格力电器总裁"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-9b6204f050416417bce28a01bd154d18_1440w.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "79 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/1898336751686218417"}}, "attached_info": "CkoIlKyY6tLvteBKEAMaCTExNDY0MTMwNSC+u6HABjAAOKMCQBJyEzE4OTgzMzY3NTE2ODYyMTg0MTd4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "19_1745417535.20882", "card_id": "Q_13592231935", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 37}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "工作中找领导被嫌烦，不找又说没反馈，我到底怎么做啊？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "已经合作 2 年了，工作性质导致有些流程不得不找上级确认，只发消息又不看，当面又觉烦，不管他了又说没反馈为什么不告诉他。到底什么意思"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-04ade12d2b00a426fa5161c90529e308_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "78 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/13592231935"}}, "attached_info": "CkEIlKyY6tLvteBKEAMaCTExMzY5Mzc4MyDJnYK+BjAAODtAE3ILMTM1OTIyMzE5MzV4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "20_1745417535.21321", "card_id": "Q_12893644822", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 17}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "一人之下里面陆瑾可以救郑子布，为什么没有救他？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "陆瑾为什么不救郑子布？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-486ecf02516e459e56063f9950d4b0ea_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "75 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F